HEADWORD: Palmigrade
<hw>Pal"mi*grade</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>palma</ets> palm of the hand + <ets>gradi</ets> to walk.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Putting the whole foot upon the ground in
walking, as some mammals.</def>⟦br⟧
